Number 25: Christopher Columbs
Christopher Columbs 1) ____ lived _________ (live) in italy. In 1492 he 2) ___ left ____ (leave) Europe
and 3) ____ travelled ____(travel) across the Atlantic Ocean by boat. After five weeks, he 4) __ reached
____ (reach) land and he 5) _____ brought _____ (bring) back gold, cotton, birds and plants to Europe.
Columbs 6) _____ made ____(make) three more voyages to this land but he 7) ___ didn’t realise ____
(not/ realise) that it 8) ___ was ____ (be) America !
Number 26: Captain Scott.
4 Form questions then use text in Ex. 3 to answer them.
1 Columbs/live/in India ?
“Did Columbus live in India ?”
“No, he didn’t. He lived in Italy.”
2 when/ he/ leave Europe ?
“When did he leave Europe ?”
“He left Europe in 1492.”
3 how long/ be / his first voyage ?
“How long was his first voyage ?”
“His first voyage was for five weeks.”
4 what/ he / bring back to Europe ?
“What did he bring back to Europe ?”
“He brought back gold, cotton, birds and plants to Europe”
